    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 21.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第21课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Mad or Not.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是不是疯了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why do people think the writer is mad?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么人们认为作者疯了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Airplanes are slowly driving me mad.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "飞机正在逐渐把我逼疯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I live near an airport and passing planes can be heard night and day.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我住在机场附近，日夜都能听到飞机飞过的声音。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "The airport was built years ago but for some reason it could not be used then.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "机场是多年前建成的，但由于某种原因，当时未能启用。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Last year, however, it came into use.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "然而，去年机场开始投入使用。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Over a hundred people must have been driven away from their homes by the noise.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "肯定已有一百多人因为噪声被迫搬离家园。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "I am one of the few people left.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我是少数留下来的人之一。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Sometimes I think this house will be knocked down by a passing plane.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有时我觉得这房子会被飞过的飞机撞倒。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I have been offered a large sum of money to go away but I am determined to stay here.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有人出一大笔钱让我搬走，但我决心留在这里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Everybody says I must be mad and they are probably right.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "人人都说我一定是疯了，他们也许说得对。"
      }
    }
  ],
